modules.description: Provides functions to process and transform streams of data, including mapping, filtering, and accumulating values. Works with custom stream types that represent sequences of operations and errors. Used to build and evaluate complex data processing pipelines in a declarative manner.

Provides functions to define and handle HTTP/JSON RPC endpoints with type-safe request and response handling. Works with custom data types, JSON encoders, and HTTP request/response structures. Used to build structured, type-checked API services in the Tezos project.

manages data processing pipelines through custom stream types, enabling transformation, filtering, and accumulation of values in a declarative style. It supports building complex operations by composing streams that handle sequences of data and errors. This module integrates with server setups to process incoming requests efficiently. For example, it can filter user input, map it to internal representations, and accumulate results for response generation.
